WEBVTT

00:00.382 --> 00:04.215
Any business that wants to realize its potential has to have good design.

00:04.774 --> 00:09.861
Good design is a part of any brand realizing its full potential in the end.

00:10.753 --> 00:13.007
The world doesn't need more mediocre products.

00:13.724 --> 00:17.059
And designers, they're all about creating great design.

00:17.466 --> 00:19.979
And it should be the same with any company, any brand.

00:20.771 --> 00:24.971
So it's really about making sure that you're creating the future.

00:25.094 --> 00:29.080
You're thinking about what's possible, not just rehashing what exists.

00:29.761 --> 00:31.116
And that's really what design is all about:...

00:31.257 --> 00:37.515
...creating products and services that really excite and delight the consumer, the user.

